definition:
A man of the Arabs living at the time of the Patriarchs, first mentioned at Gen.25.15; 
 son of: Ishmael (H3458); 
 brother of: Nebaioth (H5032), Kedar (H6938), Adbeel (H0110), Mibsam (H4017), Mishma (H4927), Dumah (H1746), Massa (H4854), Hadad (H2301), Jetur (H3195), Naphish (H5305), Kedemah (H6929) and Mahalath (H4258)
 § Tema = "desert"
1) the 9th son of Ishmael
2) the land settled by Tema the son of Ishmael
